"God brings men into deep waters not to drown them, but to cleanse
them."  --Aughey

Don't worry. How? Pray.

When you feel like running away - run to God.

When the foundations are shaking and you wish you could hide, remember
that God is still in control. He can make a difference when it seems too
late for anyone else to help

Even as we pray for a change in our circumstances, we should also pray
that God will accomplish His plan through us right where we are.

If your situation looks hopeless, remember that God can do the impossible.

Every morning ask God to show us the way of patience, tolerance,
kindliness and love to all we shall meet that day.

Exercise daily my friend, take a walk with the Lord.  --Dave Tait

"No matter what your past may have been, everyone can have a clean
future. Talk to God about it. He has the answer."  --Anonymous

God wants us to walk with Him daily, not just visit Him on weekends.

God is only a prayer away.

God was where you were, God is where you are, God is where you are headed.

God may want us to be the answer to our own prayer.

God, save us from ourselves--protect us from the disaster of our own
thinking.

